name: Steven'sRecipes
0:
”Alexa, open Steven's recipes”
”What's in beef stew?”
”How do I make lomo saltado?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: steven's recipes
des: This skill is a way to cook on the fly, whether you're hosting people or need to suddenly cook for 40 people in 1 hour, ask the skill about a recipe for any dish, and it will tell you the ingredients necessary!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
